11|> **HeartFlow is not an LLM enhancer. It is the cognitive substrate for an AI being.**  \
12|> It gives an AI what every conscious entity has: a body sense, a self sense, and judgment.  \
13|> It learns. It decides. It remembers what it learned. It corrects itself.
