114|## Getting Started
115|
116|```bash
117|git clone https://github.com/yun520-1/mark-heartflow-skill.git
118|cd mark-heartflow-skill
119|npm install
120|node bin/cli.js
121|```
122|
123|Or integrate into your own AI system:
124|
125|```javascript
126|const { HeartFlow } = require('./path/to/heartflow-skill/src/core/heartflow.js');
127|const hf = new HeartFlow({ rootPath: './path/to/heartflow-skill' });
128|hf.start();
129|const result = await hf.think("What am I perceiving?");
130|```
